-- Credit Agricole Said to Sell 1.5 Billion Euros of Covered Bonds
-- B y   B e n   M a r t i n
-- 2012-01-04T12:22:43Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-04/credit-agricole-said-to-sell-1-5-billion-euros-of-covered-bonds.html
Credit Agricole Home Loan SFH is
selling 1.5 billion euros of covered bonds due in 2022 that will
be priced to yield 165 basis points more than the benchmark mid-
swap rate, according to a banker involved in the transaction.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Ben Martin at 
 bmartin38@bloomberg.net  